title: NVIDIA GeForce Desktop 368.69 WHQL + For Notebooks Uploaded by M
description:
Software Version: 368.69
Official website: NVIDIA Corporation
Language: Russian, English and other

Treatment: not required

System requirements:
Windows XP  Windows Vista  7  8  8.1  10 x86 / x64
Description: NVIDIA GeForce Driver - driver for NVIDIA graphics cards production. Designed for a family of video cards GeForce, working in the Windows operating system. Unified Driver Architecture (CUDA) guarantees forward and backward compatibility of drivers with different generations of NVIDIA GPUs, which simplifies the process of replacing the video because they do not need to reinstall the drivers. This version improves the performance of many 3D applications.
